<div class="mt4">
  <div class="pa4 center mw8 flex items-center flex-column flex-row-ns">
    <div>
      <h1>
        Automatically import bank notifications to YNAB
      </h1>
      <p>
        Stop adding transactions manually, if your bank sends you any kind of email notification, we can help!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="center">
      <a href="#">
        Sign-up
      </a>
      <!-- <img width="50%" src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/images/undraw_cloud_sync_2aph.svg") %>" alt="Undraw Cloud Sync"/> -->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<article id="how-it-works">
  <div class="pa4 center mw8">
    <h1>How it works</h1>
    <section>
      <div>
        <h3>1. Turn on email notifications in your bank.</h3>
        <div class="">
          <div class="">
            <img width="25%" src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/images/undraw_mail_2_tqip.svg") %>" alt="Undraw Cloud Sync"/>
          </div>
          <p>
            To take advantage of YNAB It your bank needs to offer email notifications. Start by turning them on.
          </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>2. Connect YNAB.</h3>
      <div>
        <img width="25%" src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/images/undraw_authentication_fsn5.svg") %>" alt="Undraw Cloud Sync"/>
      </div>
      <p>
        After you sign-up for an account here, you need to connect
        your YNAB account with us so we can create new transactions
        on your behalf.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>3. Configure YNAB It.</h3>
      <div>
        <img width="25%" src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/images/undraw_following_q0cr.svg") %>" alt="Undraw Cloud Sync"/>
      </div>
      <p>
        We give you a special email address where you need to forward all the emails from your bank account. Moderm email services give you the ability to add this easily.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3 >4. Relax and take control of your budget.</h3>
      <img width="25%" src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/images/undraw_chilling_8tii.svg") %>" alt="Undraw Cloud Sync"/>
    </section>
  </div>
</article>
<article id="pricing">
  <div class="pa4 center mw8">
    <h1>Pricing</h1>
    <section>
      <div>
        <h3>$24/yearly (or $2.5/month)</h3>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</article>

<div class="">
  <div class="pa4 center mw8 flex items-center">
